title: Pearl Jam - Vic Theatre Chicago - August 2 2007 - 192k MP3
description:

Set List: All or None, Education, Sad, In Hiding, Parachutes, I&#039;m Open, Wishlist, Down, Undone, Off He Goes, Hard To Imagine, God&#039;s Dice, World Wide Suicide, Rats, Gone, Why Go

Encore 2: Black Diamond (a Kiss song sung by Matt and was dedicated to "Keith" a roadie for Soundgarden, Pearl Jam, Neil Young and Ben Harper), Comatose, Sonic Reducer
